‚ÄãYOLOv9 (You Only Look Once, version 9) is a significant advancement in real-time object detection, introduced in February 2024 by Chien-Yao Wang, I-Hau Yeh, and Hong-Yuan Mark Liao. It builds upon previous YOLO versions, incorporating novel architectural elements to enhance accuracy and efficiency.‚Äã
